  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/c5cac71af34349d27eb41e9b50557ee7.poster.avif?t=1679594848\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/c5cac71af34349d27eb41e9b50557ee7.webm?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/c5cac71af34349d27eb41e9b50557ee7.mp4?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore space and save humankind in AGOS : A Game of Space.<br>Travel through different star systems, build and pilot space probes, collect resources and develop the technologies you need to face the dangers of space and ultimately save humankind.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME A SPACE PILOT</h2>Experience an innovative realistic physic based gameplay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/d555210a4a86cf59326e299011b0b0ac.poster.avif?t=1679594848\" width=550 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/d555210a4a86cf59326e299011b0b0ac.webm?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/d555210a4a86cf59326e299011b0b0ac.mp4?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ANALYSE, ADAPT, EVOLVE</h2>Build your probes, unlock new parts, improve your ship to face all the dangers that space can offer to unwary travellers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/9a3deeeecaee8b68c9cce71eab6b5656.poster.avif?t=1679594848\" width=550 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/9a3deeeecaee8b68c9cce71eab6b5656.webm?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/9a3deeeecaee8b68c9cce71eab6b5656.mp4?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A UNIQUE VR EXPERIENCE</h2>Get into the cockpit, use your controllers to pilot, improve and customize your ships. Play for hours thanks to the motion sickness free system.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/e91c556b515311a2926f1cc9491e130a.poster.avif?t=1679594848\" width=550 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/e91c556b515311a2926f1cc9491e130a.webm?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/e91c556b515311a2926f1cc9491e130a.mp4?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/c5cac71af34349d27eb41e9b50557ee7.poster.avif?t=1679594848\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/c5cac71af34349d27eb41e9b50557ee7.webm?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/c5cac71af34349d27eb41e9b50557ee7.mp4?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore space and save humankind in AGOS : A Game of Space.<br>Travel through different star systems, build and pilot space probes, collect resources and develop the technologies you need to face the dangers of space and ultimately save humankind.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME A SPACE PILOT</h2>Experience an innovative realistic physic based gameplay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/d555210a4a86cf59326e299011b0b0ac.poster.avif?t=1679594848\" width=550 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/d555210a4a86cf59326e299011b0b0ac.webm?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/d555210a4a86cf59326e299011b0b0ac.mp4?t=1679594848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ANALYSE, ADAPT, EVOLVE</h2>Build your probes, unlock new parts, improve your ship to face all the dangers that space can offer to unwary travellers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1392700/extras/9a3deeeecaee8b68c9cce71eab6b5656.p